  "instructions": [
    "heat the fish stock in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "add the sliced ginger and chopped lemongrass and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "add the fish sauce, soy sauce, sugar, and salt, and stir to combine.",
    "add the chicken breast and cook until browned on all sides and cooked through.",
    "add the crushed amaretti cookies and cook for 1 minute.",
    "stir in the coconut milk and lime juice.",
    "taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "serve the pho-ga hot, garnished with chopped green onions and a sprinkle of black pepper.",
    "serve immediately and enjoy!"
